Restaurant top 10 page. This page will be all about the finest restaurants in Glasgow.
It will weigh price, user reviews and any personal experience into account when ranking it.

The page will have a pretty simple design. Focusing mostly on the restaurants themselves.

Each restaurant will have at least one image, trustpilot star rating and brief review on the page.

At the top of the "body" of the page there will be a image carousel showing extra photos of the restaurants in descending order of their ranking.
clicking on an image will send you to the div of the restaurant.

It will also include a nav bar on the top of the page, and a footer including the github page and some basic site information.